data.description: AMAZING $60,000 under market value! This charming 4-bedroom, 3-full bathrooms home is situated on a corner lot and boasts a bonus Gameroom. With an open floor plan, the primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main level. Recent updates include carpeting installed in October 2023, as well as a fresh coat of paint throughout the interior. Plus, it's just a short six houses away from the community pool, offering easy access to leisure and recreation. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! HOUSE IS SOLD AS IS.
